{"tid":43694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失魂休班警 遺失委任證及禁區許可證","createTime":"2016-12-17T16:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T15:28:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4c3d3365f6a970d0fd5df9b37fda7b8828ce6a","tid":43694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"一名天水圍分區警務人員，上周五(16日)休班期間在天水圍發現遺失一張警察委任證及一張邊境禁區許可證，遂報告上級。警方十分重視有關案件，在接獲報告後已立即展開調查，並在可能遺失有關物品的地點搜尋，暫未有發現。案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由天水圍分區跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民如拾獲該警察委任證及邊境禁區許可證，應立即致電999或把有關證件交到就近的警署。警方強調有嚴謹的機制和既定程序規管人員妥善保管警察文件，就有關事件，警方會展開內部調查，如發現有人員違規，定會嚴肅處理。"},{"pid":"898d4ba8b11d561bfdbb63044db7377c1431b6a4","tid":43694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ca77f2e90bbe29e3a61e6214f270d67c1fdbd2","tid":43694,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0169b8bcb22ed883bd3b254994286a7758448e","tid":43694,"uid":5714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02833840d1697a8d4edf79c1381137d43a20e53","tid":43694,"uid":5714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"幾時有休班警看了一下錶嘅「新聞」"},{"pid":"fa4ad7ba6090ef60294c7a0344ad3450cf520ce8","tid":43694,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a914406e42cb701d05331bd680d7085c68a1731","tid":43694,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"休班警是咪每日都會有新聞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"